perl-http-cookies (HTTP cookie jars)

HTTP::Cookies - This class is for objects that represent a
"cookie jar" -- that is, a database of all the HTTP cookies that a
given LWP::UserAgent object knows about.

HOME: https://github.com/libwww-perl/HTTP-Cookies

======================================================================
REQUIRES: perl-http-date perl-http-message 

